erage performs\nless well, but---for the fundamental mode---remains adequate for low\nfrequencies or thin layers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jan 2018 19:57:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Mar 2018 19:31:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
