plasticity model, can\nsuccessfully predict both the micro-mechanical and macro-mechanical responses\nof bearing steels while accounting for the martensitic transformation of the\nretained austenite.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jan 2018 04:32:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-18"}
